## Requirements

-   Software: [R](https://www.r-project.org//)
-   Operating system: Linux, OS X, Windows, ... (any that runs R)
-   Memory: Minimum 500 MiB of RAM. Recommended \> 1 GiB.
-   Disk space: Roughly 3-5 times the total size of your raw data files.

